data.description: This charming one-story home is a perfect blend of classic comfort and original elegance.  As you pull in, you'll notice the driveway with additional parking, a grand 3 car garage and beautiful Spanish tile roof. From the lush landscaping in the courtyard, through the mahogany and iron door, to the open spaces and cathedral ceilings with exposed wooden beams, you and your guests will have a warm welcoming.  The island kitchen adorned with granite countertops and ample counterspace are sure to suit your everyday and entertaining needs.  The home also offers a workspace located off the main living area perfect for working from home or afterschool work. Through the backdoor you'll find a quaint covered patio to enjoy your favorite beverage.  In the sought after neighborhood of Vista Villas, you'll find your new home. Foundation repaired with Allied Foundation with transferrable warranty. 3D Tour available. Seller considering all offers.
